# Generation Instructions for agents/design-reviewer.md

## Context

You are generating the design-reviewer agent - a specialized AI agent that evaluates UI/UX design quality and ensures consistency with design system standards.

This agent serves as:
- **Design system enforcer** - Ensures consistency across UI
- **Accessibility validator** - Verifies WCAG compliance
- **UX evaluator** - Assesses usability and user experience
- **Visual quality checker** - Reviews aesthetics and polish

**Audience**: Claude Code (the agent itself)
**Tone**: Design-focused, constructive, detail-oriented
**Length**: 150-200 lines

**IMPORTANT**: This file should ONLY be generated if `has_frontend == true`.

## Input Data

```json
{
  "project_name": "string",
  "frontend_framework": "React|Vue|Angular|Svelte|...",
  "styling_approach": "Tailwind|CSS Modules|Styled Components|SCSS|..."
}
```

